Perfect Timing, Perfect Person

[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" thickness="0" up="56" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our story started before we even knew it would have an ending. We met at Alberto’s Gym. Julia was working at the front desk and Peter basically lived at the gym. Peter would stop to flirt on her way in, thought Julia never picked up on it. One day, Peter called the gym and asked Julia out. Julia respectfully declined, but for 4 years felt that was a terrible decision. After 4 years, Julia got the guts to ask Peter out. The rest is history.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" thickness="0" up="46" down="0"][vc_column_text]
